#. TRANSLATION: ppsspp
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid ""
"The PSP will cull triangles that are outside a 4096x4096 clipping box, and "
"also triangles crossing the Z=1 plane if clipping is enabled."
msgstr ""
"El PSP sacrificarà triangles que estan fora d'una caixa de retall 4096x4096, "
"i també triangles que creuen el pla Z=1 si el retall està activat."

#. TRANSLATION: mupen64plus
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid ""
"The area around the joystick's neutral position where input is ignored. Can "
"help reduce unintended inputs."
msgstr ""
"L’àrea del voltant de la posició neutral de la palanca on l’entrada serà "
"ignorada. Poot ajudar a reduïr entrades no intencionades."

