msgstr "El mes del teu aniversari."

#. TRANSLATION: xenia, xenia-canary
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid ""
"The sample count of every tile will be incremented on every EVENT_WRITE_ZPD "
"by this number. Setting this to 0 means everything is reported as occluded."
msgstr ""
"El recompte de mostres de cada rajola s'incrementarà en cada EVENT_WRITE_ZPD "
"amb aquest número. Establir a 0 significa que tot s'informa com a oclòs."

#. TRANSLATION: libretro/melondsds
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid "The theme colour of the emulated console."
msgstr "El color del tema de la consola emulada."

#. TRANSLATION: ppsspp
msgctxt "game_options"
msgid ""
"There is generally no point in going beyond 4x texture scaling unless you "
"are running at very high resolutions."
msgstr ""
"En general, no té sentit anar més enllà de l'escalat de textura 4x tret que "
"s'estigui executant a resolucions molt altes."

